snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We‚Äôre updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

American Sign Language: https://www.youtube.com/live/W3uQA_unm0I
British Sign Language: https://youtube.com/live/ZygMYm2sx5U
Audio Descriptions: https://youtube.com/live/DoXrLv__PAY

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!  
https://www.minecraft.net/

–¢—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä 7-—ó —Å–µ—Ä—ñ—ó 2-–≥–æ —Å–µ–∑–æ–Ω—É "–ú–∏—Ä–æ—Ç–≤–æ—Ä—Ü—è". –ó–ª–∞ –õ—ñ–≥–∞ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ, –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –±–∞–Ω–¥–∏ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ. –ù–∞—Å–ª—ñ–¥–∫–∏ 6-—ó —Å–µ—Ä—ñ—ó 2-–≥–æ —Å–µ–∑–æ–Ω—É "–ú–∏—Ä–æ—Ç–≤–æ—Ä—Ü—è". –ö–∞–º–µ–æ –õ–µ–∫—Å–∞ –õ—é—Ç–æ—Ä–∞ –∑ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–æ–º, –ö—Ä–∏–∑–∞ –Ω–∞ –ó–µ–º–ª—ñ X "–§–ª–µ—à", –Ü–≥–ª—ñ –ü–∞—É–µ—Ä—Å, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –∫—ñ–Ω—Ü—ñ–≤–∫–∏, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –î–≤–µ—Ä–µ–π –ú—É–ª—å—Ç–∏–≤—Å–µ—Å–≤—ñ—Ç—É, –†—ñ–∫ –§–ª–µ–≥, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –∫–∞–Ω–æ–Ω—É –ó–∞–≥–æ–Ω—É —Å–∞–º–æ–≥—É–±—Ü—ñ–≤. –ß–∞—Ä—ñ–≤–Ω–∏—Ü—è, –î–∂–æ–∫–µ—Ä, –ë–µ–Ω –ê—Ñ—Ñ–ª–µ–∫, –∑–º—ñ–Ω–∏ –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω–∞, –•–∞—Ä–ª—ñ –ö–≤—ñ–Ω–Ω, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –∫—ñ–Ω—Ü—ñ–≤–∫–∏, —Å—Ü–µ–Ω–∞ –ø—ñ—Å–ª—è —Ç–∏—Ç—Ä—ñ–≤. –§–ª–µ—à–±–µ–∫–∏ –ø—Ä–æ –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω–∞, –ø–æ—è—Å–Ω–µ–Ω–Ω—è –ø–æ—Å–∏–ª–∞–Ω—å –Ω–∞ –ë–µ—Ç–º–µ–Ω–∞ —Ç–∞ “ê–æ—Ç–µ–º-–°—ñ—Ç—ñ. –ë–∞–Ω–¥–∞ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ, –°—É–ø–µ—Ä–º–µ–Ω, –õ—ñ–≥–∞ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç—ñ. –ó–º—ñ–Ω–∏ —É 1 —Å–µ–∑–æ–Ω—ñ –∑—ñ —Å—Ü–µ–Ω–æ—é –∑ –§–ª–µ—à–µ–º —Ç–∞ –ê–∫–≤–∞–º–µ–Ω–æ–º, –ó–µ–ª–µ–Ω–∏–º –õ—ñ—Ö—Ç–∞—Ä–µ–º, –Ø—Å—Ç—Ä—É–±–æ–º, –ú–∞–∫—Å–≤–µ–ª–ª–æ–º –õ–æ—Ä–¥–æ–º. –ú—É–ª—å—Ç–∏–≤—Å–µ—Å–≤—ñ—Ç–Ω—ñ–π –∫—Ä–æ—Å–æ–≤–µ—Ä, –ø–µ—Ä–µ–∑–∞–≤–∞–Ω—Ç–∞–∂–µ–Ω–Ω—è DCEU —Ç–∞ DCU, –∂–∞—Ä—Ç–∏ —Ç–∞ –ø–æ—Å–∏–ª–∞–Ω–Ω—è. –¢—Ä–µ–π–ª–µ—Ä 5 —Å–µ—Ä—ñ—ó 2 —Å–µ–∑–æ–Ω—É "–ú–∏—Ä–æ—Ç–≤–æ—Ä—Ü—è".

–¢–∏–∑–µ—Ä ¬´–ë—ç—Ç–º–µ–Ω–∞: –•—Ä–∞–±—Ä–∞—è —Å–µ—Ä–¥—Ü–µ–º¬ª –∏ ¬´–°–º–µ–ª–æ–≥–æ¬ª –∏ –Ω–æ–≤—ã–π –ë—ç—Ç–º–µ–Ω –±—É–¥—É—Ç –∞–Ω–æ–Ω—Å–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–Ω—ã –≤ —Å–ª–µ–¥—É—é—â–µ–º –≥–æ–¥—É. –í —Å–ª–µ–¥—É—é—â–µ–º –≥–æ–¥—É –±—É–¥—É—Ç –∞–Ω–æ–Ω—Å–∏—Ä–æ–≤–∞–Ω—ã —Ç–∏–∑–µ—Ä ¬´–ë—ç—Ç–º–µ–Ω–∞: –•—Ä–∞–±—Ä–∞—è —Å–µ—Ä–¥—Ü–µ–º¬ª –∏ –Ω–æ–≤—ã–π ¬´–ë—ç—Ç–º–µ–Ω¬ª. –ù–∞—Ç–∞–Ω –§–∏–ª–ª–∏–æ–Ω, –ó–µ–ª—ë–Ω—ã–π –§–æ–Ω–∞—Ä—å, –û—Ä–ª–∏—Ü–∞, –ú–∏—Å—Ç–µ—Ä –¢–µ—Ä—Ä–∏—Ñ–∏–∫ –∏ –¥—Ä—É–≥–∏–µ –Ω–æ–≤—ã–µ –ø–µ—Ä—Å–æ–Ω–∞–∂–∏ –õ–∏–≥–∏ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç–∏. –ü–æ—á–µ–º—É ¬´–ù–æ–≤–∞—è –õ–∏–≥–∞ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç–∏¬ª –±–æ–ª—å—à–µ –æ—Å–Ω–æ–≤–∞–Ω–∞ –Ω–∞ –∞–Ω–∏–º–∞—Ü–∏–æ–Ω–Ω–æ–π –∫–æ–º–∞–Ω–¥–µ –õ–∏–≥–∏ –°–ø—Ä–∞–≤–µ–¥–ª–∏–≤–æ—Å—Ç–∏.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

How I "DIED" on a Hardcore Minecraft SMP

inspired by @4CVIT's naked and afraid series!

thank you to:  @Boosfer @loppezz @FlameFragsMC eggchan @LettuceK @Twirps as well as all of the capital city guards and merchant city players!

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of my music is by AZALI so check him out!)
https://www.youtube.com/@nombra101 (song during the first flame fight!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

snippet.title: BELLES VILLAIN SONG (Pt 2) - Reclaim My Story | Official Animatic Video | by Lydia the Bard & Frost
snippet.description:
BELLES VILLAIN SONG (Part 2) - Reclaim my Story | Official Animatic Music Video | By Lydia the Bard and Frostudio Chambersonic

STREAM SONG HERE - https://ffm.to/bellepart2
PRESAVE MY DEBUT ALBUM - https://ffm.to/thewoodsdebutalbum.OYD
WATCH PART 1 - https://youtu.be/xFByIo6nujM?si=oM01ONNnR-3IXosb

It‚Äôs the last Villain song for a little while now! (Don‚Äôt worry they‚Äôll be back) I hope you enjoy this extension to Belles story! It felt like Gaston for sure needed dealing with after the last one! Following this release the next thing I‚Äôll be posting is my album AAAHH

If you dont already know I‚Äôm releasing my debut album ‚ÄòThe Woods‚Äô on October 11th!! SO EXCITED I CANT EVEN BEGIN TO SAY HOW EXCITED I AM FOR YOU TO HEAR IT AAAHAHAHAH. You can presave here - https://ffm.to/thewoodsdebutalbum.OYDhttps:/ Also I hope you enjoyed the conclusion to Figs restaurant dream story aswell!! I think I‚Äôll open him a restaurant either way. Now enough waffle, the story!

BELLES VILLAIN STORY 

Belle was always the odd one out, the outcast, the outsider. Her whole life she put up with those in her village making fun of her and her Father, so she stayed hidden behind her books. Biding her time. Waiting for the right moment.

That time finally arrived when she was kidnapped by the beast, just another man trying to control her, to tame her. She‚Äôd put up with that from Gaston for years and so another man mistreating her was nothing new. The beast found that out very quickly. Belle didn‚Äôt allow herself to fall in love with him, only let the beast think that. And when her time finally claim she plucked every last petal off that rose and watched as he became a Beast forever. You might question, why, if the beast was now a monster, did he not then attack Belle? Well, that would‚Äôve happened, but Belle wasn‚Äôt just anyone, Belle had the blood of the women who cast that curse running through her veins. Belle was the enchantresses daughter. 

Now with a Beast ready to attack anyone she willed Belle sets her sights on the town, on Gaston, on her father. snippet.title: Borderlands 4 | Official New Vault Hunter Teaser: C4SH
snippet.description:
‚ñ∫ Buy Borderlands 4 Now: https://2kgam.es/Borderlands4

A roll of the dice, a flip of a card, a spin of the bullets in a chamber‚Äîthese are among the random chances that fascinate C4SH, the first of two new Vault Hunters coming to Borderlands 4.
Revealed during the Borderlands 4 panel at Tokyo Game Show 2025, C4SH is included in the first Story Pack, Mad Ellie and the Vault of the Damned, which is planned to launch in Q1 2026. This Story Pack is one of many additions outlined in our Post-Launch Roadmap, and features multiple main and side missions set in a new zone of Kairos, the brand-new Vault Hunter C4SH, new gear to earn, and a bunch of new cosmetics to collect.

Here are the ways you can add C4SH to your Vault Hunter roster when he's available in Q1 2026:
üé≤ Own (or upgrade to) the Borderlands 4 Super Deluxe Edition
üé≤ Own the Vault Hunter Pack (included in Super Deluxe Edition)
üé≤ Own Story Pack 1: Mad Ellie and the Vault of the Damned (included in Vault Hunter Pack)

Animation by Rupert Gruber - a freelance Illustrator and Art Director from Munich, currently based in Copenhagen. Check out his work here: https://www.instagram.com/rupert.gruber/

Learn more about C4SH: 
https://borderlands.2k.com/borderlands-4/news/c4sh-vault-hunter-teaser/
--------------------------------------------

Borderlands 4 is a mayhem-fueled looter shooter, jam-packed with billions of weapons, outrageous enemies, and intense co-op action. Explore a dangerous hidden planet Kairos as one of four new badass Vault Hunters.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

snippet.title: The BIGGEST WIN I'VE EVER Had on the Slot Machine that Started Lady luck HQ!
snippet.description:
BIGGEST WIN of my Life on the Slot That Started Lady Luck HQ 6 Years Ago!
 My BIGGEST WIN EVER on the Game That Made Me Love Gambling! Welcome back to Lady Luck HQ! Today we are playing some casino slots, hoping for a big win on the slot machine. We are excited to play and chase that jackpot. Get ready for the excitement! Lady Luck HQ is at the Venetian Hotel & Casino in Las Vegas. Today we are playing onHot Pots, Dragon Link, Pharo and Pin ball High Limit Slot Machine. We are all over the casino today with our friends trying to find the loosest slot machines. We even play some of my old favs and we end up winning a fortune today. 

More about us.... Delve into the world of slot machines with us! While Las Vegas is our favorite playground, local casinos also have a piece of our heart. From the pulse-racing excitement of Dragon Link and Lightning Link to the iconic Wheel of Fortune and Video Poker, we've tried our hand at them all.

Find us in the high limit rooms, where we chase the thrill of high-stakes games. Each video captures the raw, live emotion of slot play, presented in a VLOG style. It's like having a seat next to us at the casino!

Love Vegas Vlogs? So do we! For real-time casino escapades, follow our adventures on social media. And if you're plotting your next Vegas trip, our channel might just point you to the perfect casino.

Lovie Dovie has his own channel @DudeLuck23 Give him a follow =)

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 - Vault Hunter Teaser: C4SH
snippet.description:
‚ñ∫ Buy Borderlands 4 Now: https://2kgam.es/Borderlands4

A roll of the dice, a flip of a card, a spin of the bullets in a chamber‚Äîthese are among the random chances that fascinate C4SH, the first of two new Vault Hunters coming to Borderlands 4.

Revealed during the Borderlands 4 panel at Tokyo Game Show 2025, C4SH is included in the first Story Pack, Mad Ellie and the Vault of the Damned, which is planned to launch in Q1 2026. This Story Pack is one of many additions outlined in our Post-Launch Roadmap, and features multiple main and side missions set in a new zone of Kairos, the brand-new Vault Hunter C4SH, new gear to earn, and a bunch of new cosmetics to collect.

Here are the ways you can add C4SH to your Vault Hunter roster when he's available in Q1 2026:
üé≤ Own (or upgrade to) the Borderlands 4 Super Deluxe Edition
üé≤ Own the Vault Hunter Pack (included in Super Deluxe Edition)
üé≤ Own Story Pack 1: Mad Ellie and the Vault of the Damned (included in Vault Hunter Pack)

üîπ Animation by Rupert Gruber - a freelance Illustrator and Art Director from Munich, currently based in Copenhagen. Check out his work here: https://www.instagram.com/rupert.gruber/

--------------------------------------------

Borderlands 4 is a mayhem-fueled looter shooter, jam-packed with billions of weapons, outrageous enemies, and intense co-op action. Explore a dangerous hidden planet Kairos as one of four new badass Vault Hunters.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

--------------------------------------------

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

Het is uniek omdat vrijwel alles op ROBLOX is ontworpen en gebouwd door leden van de community. ROBLOX is ontworpen voor 13- tot 18-jarigen, maar staat open voor mensen van alle leeftijden. Apa itu Roblox? ROBLOX adalah taman bermain dan lokakarya virtual daring, tempat anak-anak dari segala usia dapat berinteraksi, berkreasi, bersenang-senang, dan belajar dengan aman. Keunikannya adalah hampir semua hal di ROBLOX dirancang dan dibangun oleh anggota komunitas. ROBLOX dirancang untuk anak usia 13 hingga 18 tahun, tetapi terbuka untuk semua usia. Setiap pemain memulai dengan memilih avatar dan memberinya identitas. Mereka kemudian dapat menjelajahi ROBLOX ‚Äî berinteraksi dengan orang lain melalui obrolan, bermain gim, atau berkolaborasi dalam proyek kreatif. Setiap pemain juga diberikan lahan mereka sendiri yang belum dikembangkan beserta kotak peralatan virtual untuk merancang dan membangun apa pun ‚Äî entah itu gedung pencakar langit yang dapat dilayari, helikopter yang berfungsi, mesin pinball raksasa, gim multipemain "Capture the Flag", atau kreasi lain yang belum terbayangkan. Tidak ada biaya untuk sebidang lahan virtual pertama ini. Dengan berpartisipasi dan membangun hal-hal keren, anggota ROBLOX dapat memperoleh lencana khusus serta dolar ROBLOX ("Robux"). Sebagai imbalannya, mereka dapat berbelanja di katalog daring untuk membeli pakaian dan aksesori avatar serta material bangunan premium, komponen interaktif, dan mekanisme kerja.

The Oddlaws Dark RP event is a private server we set up to goof around with our friends. 
https://oddlaws.org for a list of (most) people who joined!

The Clip Dimension:
https://youtu.be/OdLfx_DPoWI?si=Q8W3FXphpSvpTATx
I'm gonna be uploading random videos on this channel!

This event wouldn't have been possible without the hard work of these fine individuals:
https://www.twitch.tv/criken
https://www.twitch.tv/ggqf
https://x.com/PapaWasTaken
https://www.twitch.tv/sput
https://www.twitch.tv/tech
https://www.twitch.tv/walruskingdev

Season 1 Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLrHD6h2xuacP8U1CDXGHgStasPJO153fk

My links:
https://www.youtube.com/@CharborgsClips
https://www.twitch.tv/charborg
https://www.youtube.com/@UCNM3W16DLgPc6NR1xHs5xbw 
https://www.youtube.com/@charbeats

snippet.title: How to Beat DARK SOULS 1 With Only Spears
snippet.description:
Criminally underrated, the spears in Dark Souls are actually surprisingly good.
With lots of variation and unique mechanics, I'm confused why they don't get more love.
Can you beat Dark Souls 1 with only spears? Absolutely.
Now let's talk about the best way to do it.

|| SHOUTOUTS ||
@OGSckorpiion for their video on how to skip the Asylum Demon.
Take that, semantics!

snippet.title: LTA Championship Weekend - Texas | 100T vs VKS
snippet.description:
Split 3 marks the Road to the LTA Championship, starting with an all-new format where our teams will Pick a Fight and choose their opponents to start the split, before the Elimination Phase begins and we're All-Fearless Best of Five's All-the-Time! Every game is on the live patch, and every game counts. Watch Split 3 of the LTA North live to find out which team will conquer the conference, fight against LTA South for the LTA Championship, and earn a berth to Worlds 2025. For more info about Split 3, including format breakdowns and other updates, check out our Split 3 Primer.

Catch the LTA every Saturday and Sunday:
LTA Cross Conference begins at 1PM PT / 3PM MT / 4PM ET / 6PM BT

LTA North teams include Cloud9 Kia, FlyQuest, Team Liquid, Dignitas, Shopify Rebellion, LYON, Disguised, and 100 Thieves.
LTA South teams include Fluxo W7M, Furia, Isurus, Leviatan, LOUD, paiN Gaming, RED Canids Kalunga, and Vivo Keyd Stars.

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at https://lolesports.com/en-US?leagues=lta_n,lta_s
Follow us:

https://twitter.com/ltanorth
https://instagram.com/ltanorth
https://tiktok.com/@ltanorth
https://discord.gg/LTANorth

This is Minecraft, but Steve is learning the Sad Story of the DEER! When Steve discovers the Deer‚Äôs story tied to a scientists and all the other children, showing the past of the Deer kid. He needs to discover their secrets and mysteries! This is The Sad Story of the DEER in Minecraft...
__

üëãüèº Checkpoint Website: https://checkpointmultiverse.com/
üì∏ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/checkpoint.yt
‚ù§Ô∏è Connect With Us: https://direct.me/checkpointmultiverse
üßëüèº‚Äçü§ù‚Äçüßëüèº Join the Community on Discord: https://discord.gg/jkfV7mSxB6

üéµ Additional Music provided by Epidemic Sound: https://www.epidemicsound.com/

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‚Ä£ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬¨

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects‚Äîmainly cubes‚Äîthat are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

#Checkpoint #Minecraft

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: ULTRAKILL 94 - Deathcatcher
snippet.description:
Deathcatchers are a rare enemy that causes all nearby dead foes to get resurrected until it's destroyed.
The resurrected versions are slightly slower and weaker, but as the dead stack up, their numbers can easily become overwhelming.
